*usermode-1.92 (15 Jul 2007)

  15 Jul 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  +usermode-1.92.ebuild:
  Bump. Preserve app exit code, use less memory, don't use PAM data after
  free, support 'user', 'users', LABEL and UUID in usermount/userformat, add a
  dialog caption when changing password, fix GUI=no, preserve env vars in
  consolehelper if configured, fix non-UTF8 hangs, and more.

*usermode-1.87 (30 Oct 2006)

  30 Oct 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  +usermode-1.87.ebuild:
  Bump. (#153395) desktop-file-utils-0.11 enforces valid categories, so sed
  out invalid ones.

*usermode-1.86 (05 Sep 2006)

  05 Sep 2006; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>; +metadata.xml,
  +usermode-1.86.ebuild:
  Tools for certain user account management tasks

